{"tid":829911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國宣佈制裁中國軍隊裝備發展部及其部長","createTime":"2018-09-20T22:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T09:41:10.000Z","uid":141151,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a61d8105c221b6e7a767b3ceb25228502a8774e0","tid":829911,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T22:25:31.000Z","msg":"美國宣佈制裁中國軍隊裝備發展部及其部長<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/US-CHINA-RUSSIA-MILITARY-SANCTIONS-20180920/4580190.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2FUS-CHINA-RUSSIA-MILITARY-SANCTIONS-20180920%2F4580190.html&d=05Nod63SsUJ3W1ecdT50tMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=cd8ce209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/US-CHINA-RUSSIA-MILITARY-SANCTIONS-20180920/4580190.html</a><br />\n<br />\n華盛頓 &mdash; <br />\n美國在星期四宣佈對中國軍隊的裝備發展部及其部長李尚福中將實施制裁，原因是從俄羅斯購買國防裝備，從而違反了美國在2017年簽署的範圍廣泛的制裁法案。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院官員說，有關制裁立即生效。美國政府說，中國中央軍委裝備發展部與俄羅斯國防產品出口公司進行了&ldquo;重大交易&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院說，中國購買了俄羅斯的蘇-35戰機和S-400地對空導彈相關設備。<br />\n<br />\n這批軍購違反了美國2017年通過的制裁法律﹐該項法律的目的是為了懲罰俄羅斯干預2016年的美國總統選舉。法律要求制裁任何與俄羅斯國防產業從事&ldquo;重大交易&rdquo;的第三方。<br />\n<br />\n這是美國第一次利用這部制裁法律懲罰俄羅斯軍事裝備的外國買家。"},{"pid":"5e9dbf8ebae25d4af0027f2d17a4181e11a59d87","tid":829911,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T22:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a767707268715bd8f8521877afbefa5c2d28d3","tid":829911,"uid":183601,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T22:35:13.000Z","msg":"仲爽撚過J 三上悠亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw實你老母施"},{"pid":"465be234b154c3cac71ea65e02790cc9bcb041ff","tid":829911,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T